title: Gettings Creek Rest Area temporary closure
text:
OTE Home > News > News & Press > Gettings Creek Rest Area temporary closure Gettings Creek Rest Area temporary closure 
Posted on: August 2nd,   
Sunday, August 2, 2015, 1:45 p.m. 
Traveler alert: Gettings Creek Rest Area closed to traffic. Electrical issues are causing problems with the water flow. We hope to have the repairs made sometime on Monday. Thank you for your patience. Share this post:
